    "dominantPhase": "Mid Game",
    "description": "She has workable early poke/clear via Lantern Flare stacking, but her threat is much higher once Ultimate gives blink + shield to safely set up captures. Mid-game teamfights are her peak because she can repeatedly stack, capture, and reposition enemies; late remains strong with pen/AP, though she becomes more reliant on positioning against burst and hard engage."
